data.title: Al Pacino is 78 today
data.text:
(AP) — Celebrity birthdays for April 25:

Actor Al Pacino is 78.

“Dancing With The Stars” judge Len Goodman is 74.

Bassist Stu Cook of Creedence Clearwater Revisited is 73.

Singer Bjorn Ulvaeus of ABBA is 73.

Actor Jeffrey DeMunn (“The Green Mile”) is 71.

Actress Renee Zellweger is 49.

Actress Sara Paxton is 30.

Actress Allisyn Ashley Arm (Sonny With A Chance) is 22.

Singer Michael Kogel (Los Bravos) is 74.

Actress Talia Shire is 73.

Soprano Rosemarie Landry is 72.

Drummer Steve Ferrone (Tom Petty & the Heartbreakers) is 68.

Hockey Hall of Fame goalie Vladislav Tretiak is 66.

Country singer-songwriter Rob Crosby is 64.

Rock vocalist Fish (born Derek William Dick), formerly of Marillion, is 60.

Singer Andy Bell of Erasure is 54.

Actress Melonie Diaz is 34.
